Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動了獨立戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場人稱黑色叛亂的內亂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.31,0:00:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在歷史上 以日本的二度敗北落下帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本該死去的恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自稱ZERO的男子出現在11區
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率領武裝集團黑色騎士團的ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其真面目正是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被布里塔尼亞帝國所遺棄的皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修·蘭佩洛奇
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,0)}被囚禁 的 學園
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此再次宣佈 成立日本合眾國
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這一瞬間開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間就是日本合眾國第一塊領土
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不問人種 主義 宗教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為國民的資格只有一條
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是行使正義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來取ZERO的性命了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是電話 而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直聯絡不到你 擔心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 在安全的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在演說的ZERO 是別人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你現在在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢 我才要問你現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維蕾塔老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修已經回學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要補習了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也早點回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話打完了？孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是完了 各種意義上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色騎士團殘黨與自稱ZERO的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在仍據守在中華聯邦總領事館中的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是請大家放心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾弗德代理總督已代替負傷的卡拉雷斯總督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率軍將領事館重重包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此可以說租界安全已得到保證
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的騷動啊 魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己領土之中突然建了個國
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個國家還向自己宣戰了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾時替換的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演說前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音是錄音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現的時候就已經換人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟魔術表演一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人不爽 連我們都瞞著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我們」？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「我」才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修 開爐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白奶油醬（Bechamel Sauce）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意大利冰淇淋（Gelato）另盛一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷迭香（Rosemary）拿出來放冰沙（Sorbet）裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後德國酸菜（Sauerkraut）放蒔蘿籽（Dillseed）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑森林蛋糕（Schwarzwalder Kirschtorte）…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不定啦 那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有我這麼多事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊 利瓦爾是味癡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅長細緻活是吧 我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼老實多好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種角色本該沒生活能力才正常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還寫家計簿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要毛巾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長 能問一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能答不上來 不過你問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 是我和羅洛的生還紀念派對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虧你們能從恐怖襲擊中生還
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉可擔心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「要是魯魯死了 那我…」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 羅洛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有叫他來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你知道他跟哥哥不同 比較純樸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣才交不到朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫做文靜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 沾到身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都弄得粘糊糊的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不記得娜娜莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是妹妹被假弟弟替換了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅篡改了我的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還把學生會的所有人都當成玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴別塔事件以後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修·蘭佩洛奇並未顯示出特別的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校內有180個隱藏攝像頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便衣的監視人員也有47名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視人員是48名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也沒有情報顯示卡爾塔哥隊的全滅與魯路修有關
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有使用Geass的空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若他是ZERO 再潛回學校也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 C.C.到底在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若未和魯路修接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在總領事館的可能性也很低
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 和事件前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行蹤不明？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們機密情報局將繼續執行C.C.捕獲作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各員 和以往一樣繼續監視誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方中樞是監視數據的接收方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪去大家有關娜娜莉的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為知道娜娜莉不會出現在學校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 布里塔尼亞皇帝很可能掌握著娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是連親生兒女都會當工具利用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若知道我的記憶…知道我已恢復ZERO的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能魯莽行事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要欺瞞 騙過監視我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的課也要乖乖去上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就那麼沒信用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維蕾塔·紐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾中過我Geass的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Geass對一個人只能用一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 Geass對她已沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就從本不該存在的弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先從這傢伙開始溫柔地攻略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左翼德意志州軍開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷蘭工兵 制壓地雷區
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右翼的意大利州軍也撐住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來今晚的波爾多（Bordeaux）將是勝利的美酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正上方出現未確認機體1架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞的白色死神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓桌騎士來前線了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負已定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下武器的人 本人不會攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打下來 敵人只有一架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想繼續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 單獨作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木本來就是殿下的部下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是第七騎士（Knight of Seven）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下的直屬部下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該為他的榮升感到高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界現在還充滿悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他有身為路標的自覺和責任感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟被朱雀帶走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼想起看相冊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是學生會馬拉松舞會的文檔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長太熱衷搞活動也真讓人頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 失戀比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催人淚下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是會長把獎盃交給優勝的利瓦爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你能逃出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聞播了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴別塔被軍方完全包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是怎麼突破包圍圈的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是「怎樣從恐怖分子手中逃出來的」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有緊急通道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想通知你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那種情況下手機不通
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了 那掛墜盒是我給他的生日禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 10月25日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是娜娜莉的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 那個掛墜盒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想 給男生掛墜盒有點那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該給你別的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這是你給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 魯路修的監視情況無變化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全無使用過Geass的形跡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚Geass的詳情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教團的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在談話嗎 我稍後再來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是執行同一任務的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的指使…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能被聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東京管區也是只有我們才知道的機密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你這樣殺了多少隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最確實迅速的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本合眾國成立後已過了三天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞不可能這樣一直僵持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中華聯邦本國 也有總領事更替的動向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還沒收到魯路修的下一步指示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已推遲了布里塔尼亞發來的引渡交涉要求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計能撐一周
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會轉告ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是中華聯邦政府的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想來 你扮兔女郎不是更直截了當嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是…女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也暴露得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒幽默感的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:12:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拿ZERO當遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸會 紅月卡蓮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是紅蓮二式的機師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你們有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 扇先生他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到嗎 ZERO啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是科奈莉婭·R·布里塔尼亞公主的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾伯特·G·P·吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天15時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將對犯下叛國罪的特一級罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,256人進行處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你珍惜部下的的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和我堂堂正正決一勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾弗德 真有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 就魯魯一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是夏莉你 游泳部怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被抓來負責買生日禮物了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顧問維蕾塔老師的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家說我也老惹她生氣 正好做個人情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不擅長選禮物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是買酒吧 看她好像喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是品種什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪你去選禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝提供素材
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這能抑制你那失控的Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若只是屏蔽光信息就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那普通的彩色隱形眼鏡也行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:14:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別試探我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所知 這是特製的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 若你的Geass變得比現在更強…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前我會做個了結的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去幫忙選禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維蕾塔老師要過生日了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 生日是很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅～洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 你也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是交流
