Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就當是約會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過竟連羅洛也拖來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真像會長的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來能成為男女交流生態學會演講的好材料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此就拖人家來跟蹤哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛也有興趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會成為親人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對像通過預測路線Z（Zebra）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 和7班交換
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2班進行警戒準備與C.C.接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始周邊清理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是ZERO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地在巴別塔設下了陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 敵人不是租界的總督府
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖不知道誰是監視者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但系統本身有漏洞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會對明天部下的處刑坐視不理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶還是沒有恢復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 這裡該怎麼寫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 能勞駕一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想坐一次纜車來著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我夏莉才會失去記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還擅自篡改了會長和利瓦爾的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一切結束之後 一定讓你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長他們跟著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標即將進店
