Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO都復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聲點 會被客人們發覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
