Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配置不變 準備與C.C.接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,條件已成熟
